                <h3>Jio Fiber</h3>
                <p>Jio Fiber is nationally the most recognised fiber brand and offers high speeds — their plans go up to 1 Gbps in fully deployed areas. However, in Bilimora, Jio's fiber network coverage is not as comprehensive as in major cities. Their entry-level plans start around ₹699–799/month (billed monthly), which is significantly more expensive than Nisan's annual equivalent.</p>
